{"tid":2270536,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉發]拜登真係輸緊？","createTime":"2020-11-04T05:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T19:00:23.000Z","uid":302895,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ac1a4a523ca37114b336094f8f5572137598e638","tid":2270536,"uid":302895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:40:40.000Z","msg":"[圖中數據截至12:51 pm]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JS9Canz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJS9Canz.jpg&h=234e0956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/elections/2020/general-results\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Felections%2F2020%2Fgeneral-results&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3Vcyq%2BFBM5c0LZ9Ts2TrilmEa4%3D&h=572d9b55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Felections%2F2020%2Fgeneral-results&h=966669df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/elections/2020/general-results</a><br />\n<br />\n看連登看燈神不如看數據，第一次寫這種文，純粹是覺得是次大選空前刺激空前關注，小弟才疏學淺，如果有錯還望指出。<br />\n<br />\n如何理解圖二與大選規則？<br />\n1.\t勝者全取，即該州得票較多者，全取所有選舉人票(州名下面的數字就是該州的選票人票數量)。<br />\n2.\t總選舉人票超過半數（即270張）就可當選。截至12:51，特朗普只有148票；而拜登有223票。<br />\n3.\t圖中深藍色代表拜登已取州份，圖中深紅色代表特朗普已取州份。<br />\n4.\t圖中淺藍色代表拜登暫時領先該州份，圖中淺紅色代表特朗普暫時領先該州份。<br />\n5.\t紅框是我自己加的，是指特朗普領先的州份，但是不領先超過10萬票。<br />\n6.\t白色的州份是在點票(我不肯定)。<br />\n<br />\n小分析(其實都無咩好分析)：<br />\n特朗普在NC「只」領先八萬，如果特朗普也取下了NC，以及其他紅框以外的淺紅州(有此合理假設因為紅框以外的淺紅州都領先至少十萬)，更別說有些州是領先四五十萬，那裡加總起來已經超過270張選舉人票。<br />\n反觀拜登，把紅框(NC以外)、淺藍、白色的州份都算給他，那裡也只有255張選舉人票，更何況紅框都是特朗普領先。<br />\n<br />\n所以我會說，NC是關鍵州份，特朗普得票暫時為273萬，而拜登為265萬，前者領先8萬。<br />\n<br />\n就讓我們拭目以待吧，但不論誰當選也好，請時刻裝備好自己。<br />\n<br />\nFollow Instagram : @thinking_bro<br />\n<br />\n------13:21更新------<br />\n特朗普已取TX及IA(紅框)，拜登已取HI(白色)，選舉人票目前是227比210，拜登領先。拜登總得票約六千萬，特朗普則約為五千八百萬。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">侵侵真心難輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b33e8758827956e17fda4a5b70d7c6e6de04f390","tid":2270536,"uid":302895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:41:31.000Z","msg":"好文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"e2cf0b511dca9e5902b3cb7d49f27e52ea73d6f9","tid":2270536,"uid":302895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:41:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f9074b65c3260f8b884bc20023c6fcc9a530e1","tid":2270536,"uid":302895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de7d9690947d4b9e8a63a4ff57975f4f137101c","tid":2270536,"uid":302895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8652834e1813e1a509d8cd2ea845742feaf2bf9","tid":2270536,"uid":319971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"b4881fdb5e485f4e7c678f89915e7e45310f2d76","tid":2270536,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:48:36.000Z","msg":"未驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32dee00441a94ccf70c768efddae1a0170ce1cd","tid":2270536,"uid":